{"tid":2338831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府有八千億財政儲備咁多做乜嘢好？","createTime":"2020-12-24T09:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:42:36.000Z","uid":307151,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b1826f4ca274789dd8040605916d7c7d6ab2f282","tid":2338831,"uid":307151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">八千億咁多緊係全民回水啦屌你老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今年回得個1萬蚊點撚夠呀？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗疫防疫基金又唔係真係幫到市民同僱員，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">全部俾撚晒大企業，佢地賺緊大錢仲俾佢地</span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔係真係幫到僱員，入撚晒僱主個袋到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且最新數字，貧窮人口係有<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">150萬</span></span>人！ 700幾萬人有150萬都係貧窮人口，有<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">2成</span></span>都係窮人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以宜家就要參與鄺神嘅聯署！促請財政司司長陳茂波係2021/2022嘅財政預算案每人回水最少<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"green\">1萬5千蚊</span></span>!<br />\n<br />\n等佢聽到市民嘅聲音！知道有幾撚多人要求佢全民回水！<br />\n<br />\n而且今年都派過1萬蚊，而且都係陳茂波派，行政費一定慳到！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSedHi0S1sX7WGFC1m0VqlNqTNPyGQNMHTAwddGDtoOqeS_axg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSedHi0S1sX7WGFC1m0VqlNqTNPyGQNMHTAwddGDtoOqeS_axg%2Fviewform&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D